Package fastfoodfinal

Class StaffList

java.lang.Object
fastfoodfinal.StaffList
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class StaffList extends Object implements Serializable
Represents a collection of staff members within the fast food system. Provides functionality to add, remove, update, and filter staff records.
